SEHLILE isibalo sabantu abangasebenzi kuleli sisuka ku-35,3% saya ku-34,5% ngekota yokuqala yalo nyaka. Lokhu kuvezwe ngabeStats SA ngesikhathi bekhipha izibalo zabantu abangasebenzi. Ngokusho kwalesi sikhungo, lesi sibalo sehle ngo-370 000  ku-Q1:2022 uma kuqhathaniswa nekota yesine ka-2021. [Thread]South Africaâ€™s #unemployment rate decreased by 0,8 of a percentage point to 34,5% in Q1:2022 compared to Q4:2021.#StatsSA pic.twitter.com/Tn6Vw0SIBg Kuthiwa ukwenyuka kokuqashwa kubonakale kakhulu ezimbonini eziletha izinsiza zomphakathi nezenhlalo, ezokukhiqiza nezohwebo. Yize kunjalo, isibalo sabansundu abangasebenzi sisephezulu kakhulu ngo-38,6%. Abantu abasha abaneminyaka ephakathi kuka-15-24 nabano-25-34 yibona abanesibalo esiphezulu kakhulu ngo-63,9% no-42,1%. Kuthiwa abesifazane abansundu yibona abasenkingeni kakhulu. Isifundazwe iFree State sithathwa njengesesine kwesinesibalo esiphansi kakhulu sokungaqashwa kwabantu ngo-31,1% 